    "# Place Cell Detection and Coordinate System Transformation\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "Functions contains:\n",
    "- **quadrant(a, b):** <br>\n",
    "    - *Check if two points are in the same quadrant*\n",
    "* **getAngle(a, b, c):**<br>\n",
    "    - *Calculate angle between three points*\n",
    "* **getDist(a, b):**<br>\n",
    "    - *Calculate distance*\n",
    "* ***calAngle_Dist(data, enclosure):***<br>\n",
    "    - *Calculate angle and distance between enclosure and defeated mouse <br> reference point is the center point of head of tail regarding Angle head point for Distance*\n",
    "* **fourPointTransform(pts, dwd, dht, image = None):**<br>\n",
    "    - *Transform image by its four vertice*\n",
    "* ***locCoordConvert(data, pts, dwd, dht):***<br>\n",
    "    - *Convert mouse location data to prospective coordicates after correcting coord system*\n",
    "* ***ptsCoordConvert(refPts, pts, dwd, dht):***<br>\n",
    "    - *Convert user-specified points to prospective coordicates after correcting coord system*\n",
    "* **headDir(data)**"
   ]
  },
